commit_message:
MOS-RN6.1 General OpenStack issues

Adds General OpenStack resolved and known issues to
 the MOS 6.1 Release Notes:
- [library] downtime for one of nodes with memcached causes
 delays in Horizon;
- Number of Rabbitmq queues is growing from failover to
 failover;
- Hypervisor summary shows incorrect total storage;
- Service log level AUDIT are sent to syslog as WARNING
 severity;
- [ostf] OSTF platform tests failed with random errors if
 we have no enough RAM on controller nodes;
- Add RabbitMQ heartbeat support to Pacemaker scripts.

Change-Id: I557c5c56b80aa9e7be0d7e51c3f95d1fe03fa766

