commit_message:
MOS-RN6.1 Ceilometer known and resolved issues

Adds Ceilometer known and resolved issues to the MOS 6.1 Release
Notes page:
- Ceilometer Nova *.rate pollsters not obtained;
- Swift notifications not obtained;
- ceilometer-agent-notification can't connect after rabbitmq restart;
- [fuel-library] Ceilometer's mongoDB is rapidly eating up partition
  space;
- ceilometer python client returns error response for LIST requests
  if mongodb has too much records.

Change-Id: Ib8611c7f11a0b471e275a97088d45ddd340b5890

MOS-RN6.1 Glance known and resolved issues

Adds Glance known and resolved issues to the MOS 6.1 Release Notes
page:

- Instance snapshot fails - with keystone error;
- Haproxy glance-api is DOWN, after all ceph nodes removal/addition
  and redeploy;
- New image is not uploaded if time to upload of image greater
  than time to life of keystone token;
- Image creation over glance v1 failed with permission denied error;
- can't upload image by link from slow source.

Change-Id: Iee3e9c945665784dd72ecb492bfd02a08c551f6b
